data.name: label11.ToolTip
data.value:
Choose a vertical scaling method for the graphs:
Classic Default PingTracer scaling behavior.
Zoom Graphs are zoomed vertically to fit the data within the specified limits.
Zoom Unlimited Graphs are zoomed vertically to fit the data.
Fixed Graph zoom level is fixed to show exactly the specified response time range. Does not self-adjust to fit the data.
